Gree + brings you a brand new experience for intelligent control. As a new official application software that Gree  develops specially for IoT era, it has the functions of appliances management, intelligent control, etc., which makes your life much easier.  

Function introductions:
1、Intelligent products can be easily added into Gree ecosystem for intelligent management uniformly;
2、You can control the appliance at anytime and anywhere you like;
3、You can know the status of the appliance in real time and all changes of appliance status will be reported to you immediately。
